      <h2>It all started with a …</h2><p>camera, a T1i DSLR in 2010. I took pictures of my beloved pups, a LOT of them, and found a passion. However, my creative juices really began to open up when I learned Photoshop. And then it began...Next I was curious about websites and learned HTML and CSS. From there it was Javascript and jQuery. A friend asked for search engine optimization help on his website, so I learned that too. And the passion grew.</p>
    </div> 
